---Test case 1--------
Input:
4 7
20 15 10 17

Output:
15
---Test case 2---------
Input:
5 20
4 42 40 26 46

Output:
36

=====================================

10 15 17 20
 7
20 - 7 = 13 -> index  = 1 < 1/2 still
next : 17 - (7 - (20 - 17)) = 17 - ( 7 - 3) = 17 - 4  = 13
find index from : 1 -> 2 - 1=> 1 != 13
7 = 15 - x + 17 - x + 20 -x
7 = 15 + 17 + 20 - 3x
3x = 15 + 10 + 20 = 45 / 3 = 15


4 26 40 42 46
20

2 + 6 = 8
20 - 8 = 12
12 / 2 = 6
40 - 12 = 28

---
46 - 20 = 26 -> find index = 1 < 1/2
find from 40 -> 42 :
20 = 46 -x + 42 -x
2x = 88 - 20 = 66
x = 66 / 2 = 33
